[size=5]Description[/size]
This Mod lets you quickly open the Alchemy menu with a hotkey while the inventory is open. A must have if you use alchemy a lot.

[size=5]Requirements[/size]
[list]
[*] MWSE
[/list]
[size=5]Installation[/size]
Copy [i]Data Files[/i] into your Morrowind install directory.
Or use the Mod Manager download.

[size=5]Usage[/size]
Open inventory, then press 'A', or the ModConfig assigned hotkey, to open the Alchemy menu

You can turn on and off the mod in-game using the Mod Config menu.

[size=5]Pairs Well With[/size]

[list]
[*] [b][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/morrowind/mods/58215]Alchemy Filtering[/url][/b] - another mod by me
[*] [b][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/morrowind/mods/48458]Right Click Menu Exit[/url][/b]
[*] [b][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/morrowind/mods/46283]QuickLoot[/url][/b]
[/list]
